# 1. Ignore Obsidian's operational UI and workspace caches
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/workspace-mobile.json
.obsidian/graph.json
.obsidian/appearance.json

# 2. Ignore Obsidian's local deleted files system entirely
.trash/

# 3. Optional: Ignore third-party plugin source files to keep diffs clean
# (This prevents tracking the actual JS/CSS source code of Dataview, etc.)
.obsidian/plugins/

todos.md